{"tid":1886350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［終極攬炒］一段訊息+一封信令政府癱瘓","createTime":"2020-02-19T00:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T12:18:38.000Z","uid":21678,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e28aac923513d8e78a96d113f26ba2804c351fc1","tid":1886350,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:14:33.000Z","msg":"// <br />\n我們是香港人<br />\n我們要求封關<br />\n保護香港<br />\n林鄭政府既然選擇漠視<br />\n就要自己承受後果<br />\n<br />\n我發誓，如果一旦感染武漢肺炎<br />\n便會立即把沾滿我口水鼻水的支票<br />\n寄給稅局；<br />\n亦會將被污染的匿名信<br />\n寄給特首辦、中聯辦、律政司、各區警署、保皇政黨，還有各大中資企業和機構<br />\n<br />\n達官貴人們<br />\n你們未必會接觸信件<br />\n但你們會接觸到接觸信件的人<br />\n你們會日夜憂心<br />\n因為你們永遠不會知道<br />\n哪一個同事、開過哪一封信<br />\n是由向政府報復的帶菌者寄出的<br />\n<br />\n這是武漢肺炎版的炭疽菌郵件攻擊<br />\n政府大可以譴責我們<br />\n也可以無視這段訊息<br />\n直到有一日<br />\n你們辦公室出現第一個同事出現源頭不明的感染<br />\n你們便不可能再無視我們<br />\n<br />\n我們健康的手足<br />\n也會群起發出載有污物的信件<br />\n哪封信藏有真病毒<br />\n哪封信只是幌子<br />\n根本不重要<br />\n因為每封匿名信<br />\n已經載滿著恐懼<br />\n足以叫你們每一位同事<br />\n需要請假自保<br />\n<br />\n還有<br />\n當你們無視醫護人員的訴求開始<br />\n他們便成為我們的同路人<br />\n除非香港的感染人數歸零<br />\n否則<br />\n他們任何一個<br />\n每天都有千百個機會<br />\n可以帶走病毒，再自製匿名信殺死你們<br />\n<br />\n請你耐心等待<br />\n天眼恢恢疏不漏<br />\n很快便會收到我們為你準備的禮物<br />\n<br />\n手動轉//"},{"pid":"42a51ad9a5209200a0f806f986558c0734cf5eca","tid":1886350,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:15:36.000Z","msg":"撚生存到咁耐咩"},{"pid":"64afc43c646d6f8141db767564750349e8293141","tid":1886350,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:17:05.000Z","msg":"只要夠多人傳出去<br />\n政府前線實會人心惶惶"},{"pid":"02f051d61e7a2ed231882e2c86e79ba105a08ae3","tid":1886350,"uid":49955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:18:14.000Z","msg":"我地法治既<br />\n睇落冇違法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7796e3e67e4dbf4d7567b96c5f580afba8b07989","tid":1886350,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />千祈唔好咁做，唔好推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553426d2d7480ef05a63c798985cbe6fc45f206d","tid":1886350,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:19:25.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"01aae1d08befb4e0c7b4c46be7afcf7c5bc1589d","tid":1886350,"uid":21678,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"42a51ad9a5209200a0f806f986558c0734cf5eca","tid":1886350,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:15:36.000Z","msg":"撚生存到咁耐咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awk07HZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fawk07HZ.jpg&h=d9c2f411&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71d4183aebdbb36ebcebc1fc4e0c49aac236f647","tid":1886350,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:21:06.000Z","msg":"係就靜雞雞做啦，直接掉狗屋咪搞到郵差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db2d2ece5e49eedb4f202cda58268e5ceb1d7de","tid":1886350,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:22:42.000Z","msg":"準備功夫要做足<br />\n買定郵票同信封先"},{"pid":"1d992c5aedfde4f033c6fa7f2312ae5feb68b7f4","tid":1886350,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:25:58.000Z","msg":"記得傳去TG group、品葱、IG 、FB"},{"pid":"2b343e246cd94a8e50d5b485736dc07bd0cc5144","tid":1886350,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:33:35.000Z","msg":"有冇病都好, 去政府部門借個廁所&quot;和你塞&quot;"},{"pid":"acc7030285443b439d80c7ddf32bcb429ec40967","tid":1886350,"uid":274772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e28aac923513d8e78a96d113f26ba2804c351fc1","tid":1886350,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:14:33.000Z","msg":"// <br />\n我們是香港人<br />\n我們要求封關<br />\n保護香港<br />\n林鄭政府既然選擇漠視<br />\n就要自己承受後果<